import { Box, Typography, Grid, Card, CardMedia, CardContent, Chip } from '@mui/material'
import { cofounders } from '../data/co-founders'

const AboutUs = () => (
  <Box id="about" sx={{ position: 'relative', backgroundColor: '#F3E2D4', color: '#17313E' }}>
    {/* Top wave to connect from Hero */}
    <Box
      component="svg"
      viewBox="0 0 1440 80"
      sx={{ position: 'absolute', top: 0, left: 0, width: '100%' }}
    >
      <path
        fill="#F3E2D4"
        d="M0,0 C360,100 1080,-100 1440,0 L1440,80 L0,80 Z"
      />
    </Box>

    {/* Decorative Circle */}
    <Box
      sx={{
        position: 'absolute',
        top: { xs: '10%', md: '5%' },
        left: { xs: '5%', md: '10%' },
        width: { xs: 120, md: 200 },
        height: { xs: 120, md: 200 },
        bgcolor: 'rgba(65,94,114,0.1)',
        borderRadius: '50%',
        zIndex: 0,
      }}
    />

    <Box sx={{ position: 'relative', pt: 12, pb: 8, px: { xs: 3, md: 10 } }}>
      {/* Who We Are */}
      <Typography
        variant="h3"
        sx={{
          fontFamily: "'DM Serif Display', serif",
          fontSize: { xs: '2rem', md: '3rem' },
          color: '#415E72',
          textAlign: 'center',
          mb: 2,
        }}
      >
        Who We Are
      </Typography>
      <Typography
        variant="h6"
        maxWidth={900}
        mx="auto"
        sx={{
          fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif',
          fontWeight: 300,
          fontSize: { xs: '1rem', md: '1.125rem' },
          color: '#17313E',
          textAlign: 'center',
          mb: 4,
          lineHeight: 1.6,
        }}
      >
        Odyssey of Wisdom is a youth association based in Ancient Olympia, dedicated
        to empowering Greek youth from underserved areas. We open doors to Erasmus+
        opportunitiesâ€”connecting young people with lifeâ€‘changing travel, learning, and
        cultural exchange.
      </Typography>

      {/* Vision & Activities */}
      <Typography
        variant="h4"
        sx={{
          fontFamily: "'DM Serif Display', serif",
          fontSize: { xs: '1.75rem', md: '2.25rem' },
          color: '#415E72',
          textAlign: 'center',
          mb: 2,
          mt: 6,
        }}
      >
        Our Vision & Activities
      </Typography>
      <Typography
        variant="body1"
        maxWidth={1000}
        mx="auto"
        sx={{
          fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif',
          fontWeight: 300,
          fontSize: { xs: '0.95rem', md: '1.05rem' },
          color: '#17313E',
          textAlign: 'center',
          mb: 4,
          lineHeight: 1.6,
        }}
      >
        We channel our collective Erasmus+ experiences into local and international
        initiatives across key themes:
      </Typography>

      {/* Chips */}
      <Grid container spacing={1} justifyContent="center" mb={6}>
        {[
          'Soft Skills','AI','Sustainability','Active Citizenship','European Identity',
          'Media & Communication','Entrepreneurship','Environment','Leadership',
          'Nonâ€‘formal Learning','Intercultural Dialogue','Sports'
        ].map(topic => (
          <Grid item key={topic}>
            <Chip
              label={topic}
              sx={{
                fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif',
                fontWeight: 300,
                backgroundColor: '#415E72',
                color: '#F3E2D4',
                px: 2,
                py: 0.5,
                borderRadius: '16px',
                fontSize: { xs: '0.75rem', md: '0.85rem' },
              }}
            />
          </Grid>
        ))}
      </Grid>

      {/* Founders */}
      <Typography
        variant="h4"
        sx={{
          fontFamily: "'DM Serif Display', serif",
          fontSize: { xs: '1.75rem', md: '2.25rem' },
          color: '#415E72',
          textAlign: 'center',
          mb: 2,
        }}
      >
        Meet the Founders
      </Typography>
      <Typography
        variant="body1"
        maxWidth={900}
        mx="auto"
        sx={{
          fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif',
          fontWeight: 300,
          fontSize: { xs: '1rem', md: '1.05rem' },
          color: '#17313E',
          textAlign: 'center',
          mb: 6,
          lineHeight: 1.6,
        }}
      >
        A diverse team of students and young professionals, united by our passion
        for youth empowerment, intercultural dialogue, and positive impact.
      </Typography>

      <Grid container spacing={4} justifyContent="center">
        {cofounders.map(person => (
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} key={person.name} sx={{ zIndex: 1 }}>
            <Card
              elevation={6}
              sx={{
                borderRadius: 3,
                overflow: 'hidden',
                transition: 'transform 0.3s ease',
                '&:hover': { transform: 'translateY(-8px)' },
              }}
            >
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                image={person.image}
                alt={person.name}
                sx={{
                  height: 300,
                  objectFit: 'cover',
                }}
              />
              <CardContent sx={{ px: 3, py: 2.5 }}>
                <Typography
                  variant="h6"
                  sx={{
                    fontFamily: "'DM Serif Display', serif",
                    fontSize: '1.25rem',
                    color: '#415E72',
                    mb: 1,
                  }}
                >
                  {person.name}
                </Typography>
                <Typography
                  variant="caption"
                  sx={{
                    display: 'inline-block',
                    fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif',
                    fontWeight: 600,
                    color: '#17313E',
                    mb: 1,
                  }}
                >
                  {person.role}
                </Typography>
                <Typography
                  variant="body2"
                  sx={{
                    fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif',
                    fontWeight: 300,
                    color: '#415E72',
                    mt: 1,
                    lineHeight: 1.5,
                    display: '-webkit-box',
                    WebkitLineClamp: 4,
                    WebkitBoxOrient: 'vertical',
                    overflow: 'hidden',
                  }}
                >
                  {person.bio}
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        ))}
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  </Box>
)

export default AboutUs
